This data originates from the World Radiation Monitoring Center (WRDC) Baseline Surface Radiation Network (BSRN). 

Technical metadata can be found in documents/format_manual_bsrn.pdf.

Software to work with the data can be found in the software/ folder.

Original copies can be downloaded from the BSRN website at http://www.bsrn.awi.de/en/data/
